name: R3-medication-dispense-status-for-R5
title: Cross-version VS for R3.MedicationDispenseStatus for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/medication-dispense-status|3.0.2 for use in FHIR R5. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R3 to R5.
